docs.name: Zillow Home Value Index (Cities): Top Tier - Hawthorne, NJ
docs.description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of top tier homes within the city of Hawthorne, NJ. Top tier homes are homes that fall into the top third of home values within the region. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
